		<p>Don&#8217;t know why so many people seem to have trouble with this add-in.  I&#8217;ve installed and used it for my monthly newsletters for the last few months and it&#8217;s working GREAT!  Segmented my email lists into groups of under 100 (mostly about 75-90 addresses per list) and always send them bcc, with my own address in in the &#8220;to&#8221; field (so that I know they&#8217;re being delivered properly) and send them out about every 15 minutes.  They&#8217;re delivered without a hitch.</p>
<p>The only gripe I&#8217;ve got is that it requires that my computer be left on for several hours (but of course that&#8217;s not your problem).  I&#8217;d love to see something like this that was cloud based.</p>

