<p>I can&#8217;t do anything in my add-on&#8217;s code about garbage in people&#8217;s Thunderbird profiles. Such garbage is not my add-on&#8217;s fault, and there&#8217;s no automated way to clean it up without potentially making the problem worse. It needs to be cleaned up manually by the user.</p>
