		<p>Please read the documentation <a href="#mailmerge">above</a> for using Send Later with Mail Merge. You need to specify the date as well as the time. Otherwise, the time will be interpreted as on the current day, so if it is past the time you specify the message will be considered &#8220;late&#8221; by Send Later and sent immediately.</p>

