<p>Do you have a lot of drafts in your Drafts folders?</p>
<p>Does the Send Later progress bar at the bottom of the screen go constantly, or does it only show up for a few seconds every minute or so?</p>
<p>Please follow the instructions <a href="#debug">in the user guide</a> for enabling debugging logging, and let Thunderbird run for a couple of minutes with debug logging enabled, then send me the resulting log.</p>

