		<p>Hi David,</p>
<p>The Send Later button in the toolbar is only useful if you also include the text box or date/time picker. Its purpose is to finish scheduling a message whose send time you&#8217;ve already entered, not to pop up the Send Later prompt window. I&#8217;ve updated the user guide above to reflect this.</p>
<p>Regards,</p>
<p>Jonathan Kamens</p>

