		<p>Hi Philip,</p>
<p>Sorry about the confusion. In response to your feedback, I&#8217;ve updated the user manual to make it clear that the Send Later button that comes with this add-on is only used to finish scheduling a message once you&#8217;ve already entered the send time in the text box or date/time picker.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve considered overloading the button so that if you don&#8217;t enter a time it pops up the prompt window, but I think that might be confusing to some users.</p>

