		<p>Hi, I am trying out the 4 Beta 4 version. The add on is great but I don&#8217;t like the new method of setting the time. The main issue that causes confusion is that in Europe we use the format of day/month/year and this can lead to confusion with the US method of month/day/year. In version 3 we picked the time from the menu and so avoided this confusion. </p>
